VALUES
	(40,45,'Amazon','B00OHY14CS','','Anonymous User','August Smart Lock - Keyless Home Entry with Your Smartphone','august-smart-lock','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The August Smart Lock is a device that connects to your deadbolt and connects to bluetooth, allowing you to control, lock and unlock your door, all from your phone, eliminating both the worry of forgetting your key at home, while also cutting back on the amount of things you need to carry around with you on a daily basis. Additionally, this is the only current smart lock on the market that doesn’t require you to entirely replace your current lock system, and is in fact designed to work with the deadbolt you already have installed. In short, this is a great product, with users claiming that it has a lot of potential and is following a great idea. It is also important to note however, that users claim there are still connectivity issues and give it a 3 out of 5 possible stars overall.</span></p><ul><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Smart lock that allows you to lock/unlock doors via your phone</span></li><li class=\"li1\">Blue tooth capabilities </li><li class=\"li1\">Works with almost all existing locking systems, eliminating the need to replace them in order to use the product</li></ul><br/></ul><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"August\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"ASL-1\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"TY0918\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Silver\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"2.21 X 3.26 X 3.26 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"2.5 X 5 X 9 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"1 Pound\"}]',299.99,143.98,1,'http://www.amazon.com/August-Smart-Lock-Keyless-Smartphone/dp/B00OHY14CS%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00OHY14CS','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"4.00\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":3,\"counter\":486,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/amzn.to\\/1QhKCbK\"},{\"key\":\"CNET\",\"value\":4,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.cnet.com\\/products\\/august-smart-lock\\/\",\"counter\":1}]','4.5','<blockquote><p><span id=\"seodescription\" class=\"description\">We haven\'t seen a flawless smart lock yet, but the August Smart Lock comes closer than any of its competitors thanks to its ease of use and overall<br/> polish.</span><br/></p><p>- Rich Brown , ','0','','Active','Best August Smart Lock Reviews and Comparisons','August Smart Lock Keyless Home Entry with Your Smartphone is the best thing to automatically lock or unlock your door. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews, comparisons, vs, and lowest price on the August Smart Lock.','[]','Usually ships in 24 hours','2016-01-27 03:49:27','2016-02-16 23:15:43'),
	(55,129,'Amazon','B00WBJGUA2','','Anonymous User','Nest Cam Security Camera','nest-security-cam','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Nest Cam Security Camera is a good option as far as in home security camera go. This camera offers 24/7 live streaming to your smart phone, night vision, motion and sound alerts and more. It is a good option for those who aren’t necessarily trying to be sneaky, but just want to keep an eye on their homes, and offers a lot of versatility in use. To that end, users seem to generally be in agreement that this is a helpful product, but no reliable as a security camera or baby monitor, and is better suited to keeping an eye on pets or the home in general while away.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Offers 24/7 live streaming and adjustable controls from the user’s smart phone</p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Can/will alert your phone if it detects motion or sound</p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Offers clear nighttime vision when the lights are off, in order to continue to accurately monitor goings on in your home at all times.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Nest Cam\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"NC1102ES\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"NC1102ES\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Black\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"6.6 X 3.8 X 6.5 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"3.9 X 6.6 X 6.9 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"1.8 Pound\"}]',199.00,174.41,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Nest-NC1102ES-Cam-Security-Camera/dp/B00WBJGUA2%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00WBJGUA2','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"4.25\",\"counter\":2},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4,\"counter\":1775,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Nest-NC1102ES-Cam-Security-Camera\\/dp\\/B00WBJGUA2\\/tag=\"},{\"key\":\"CNET\",\"value\":4.5,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.cnet.com\\/products\\/nest-cam\\/\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"PCMag\",\"value\":4,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.pcmag.com\\/article2\\/0,2817,2488861,00.asp\",\"counter\":1}]','4.5','<p>DIYers searching for a high-res live streaming camera really can\'t beat Nest Cam.<br/></p><blockquote><p>-Megan from CNET</p></blockquote>','0','','Active','Best Nest Cam Security Camera Reviews & Deals','The Nest Cam Security Camera is a Wi-Fi webcam that allows you to monitor your home and family. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews, comparisons, vs, and lowest price on the Nest Cam Security Camera.','[]','Usually ships in 24 hours','2016-01-26 04:55:27','2016-02-18 04:16:44'),
	(60,66,'Amazon','B000TKDQ5C','','Anonymous User','Lasko 754200 Ceramic Heater with Adjustable Thermostat','lasko-ceramic-adjustable-thermostat','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Lasko Ceramic Heater is a self-regulating ceramic space heater (with options for manual control). This space heater is a great option for those who require a little extra heat in a concentrated space, offering overheat protection, three basic heating options, (with an additional option to switch to a basic fan) and carrier handle for easy transport. Users give this product 4 out of 5 stars, claiming it is great for small rooms and easy to use.</span></p><p class=\"p1\">. Heats a small room very well (with 1500-watt high setting, 900-watt low setting, and fan-only option)</p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Includes multiple built in safety features, including, (but not limited to): automatic overheating sensors and turnoff. </p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Very easy to use and transport</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Lasko\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"754200\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"LCP-002\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Silver\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"9.2 X 7 X 6 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"7.1 X 7.9 X 10.8 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"4 Pound\"}]',35.99,16.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Lasko-754200-Ceramic-Adjustable-Thermostat/dp/B000TKDQ5C%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB000TKDQ5C','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":3.5,\"counter\":4}]','3.5','','0','','Active','Best Lasko Ceramic Heater with Adjustable Thermostat','The Lasko Ceramic Heater is a tabletop heater for your room or office. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews, comparisons, vs, and lowest price on the Lasko Ceramic Heater.','\"\"','Usually ships in 24 hou